room_title: Escape room "Locked Out!" by Unity Escape Rooms in Pomona
room_description: Youâ€™re running down an unfamiliar street. You need to hide from a pack of zombies hot on your trail. You turn the corner and see a dim light coming from an upstairs window. You jump a fence into the back yard and run as fast as you can to the back door and you start knocking. You hear a low whisper from what sounds like a little girl. She tells you she will only let you in if you find her favorite toy. You realize you have no choice but to play her game. Can you find her toy and escape the zombie horde in time?
